title: The New Adventures of Tarzan 1935 - TV Serial - Episode 1 - Starring Bruce Bennett, Ula Holt

sources.title: The New Adventures of Tarzan 1935 - TV Serial - Episode 1 - Starring Bruce Bennett, Ula Holt
sources.description:
Tarzan, Major Martling, and Ula Vale arrive in Guatemala to rescue Tarzan’s friend Lt. D’Arnot, who crashed while seeking the Green Goddess, an idol containing an explosive formula. Raglan, hired by Hiram Powers, steals Martling’s notebook and plots to seize the idol, leading Tarzan to confront natives guarding the lost city.

Directors: Edward A. Kull, Wilbur McGaugh
Writers: Edgar Rice Burroughs, Charles F. Royal, Edwin Blum
Actors: Bruce Bennett, Ula Holt, Frank Baker
